We now have a closed-loop system:

Identity: WILL NFT (Proof of Presence + Skill Tags).
Governance: Liquid Democracy (Delegation to Representatives).
Monetary Policy: Inflationary Minting (Based on goals) + Deflationary Burning (Based on project revenue).
Labor: Citizen Workforce (Hired via Smart Contracts).
Verification: Peer-to-Peer Presence (Location tech) + Random Jury Audits.
This is a radical system. It removes banks, removes corporations, removes traditional HR, and replaces them with a community consensus ledger.

